2026-05-15T18:29:10.1328747Z 224            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1329623Z 225            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1330527Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1331447Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1332215Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1333251Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1334251Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1335147Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1336369Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T18:29:10.1337087Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
